Here are some examples of using odc-stac to work with EDS data

1. How to use odc-stac to create RGB and GeoTiffs from the API stac items
[RGB And GeoTiff](https://github.com/earthdaily/EDA-Documentation/blob/gh-pages/EDS%20Compatibility%20Examples/venus-git-over-LEFR3.ipynb)

2. How to use the odc-stac for basic building detection using building footprint 
[Building detection](https://github.com/earthdaily/EDA-Documentation/blob/gh-pages/EDS%20Compatibility%20Examples/venus-denver-with-building-model.ipynb)

3. How to use odc-stac to query the sentinel-2 and Venus datasets with same criteria over Corumba and plot the NDVI comparison
[Compare Sentinel-2 and Venus NDVI](https://github.com/earthdaily/EDA-Documentation/blob/gh-pages/EDS%20Compatibility%20Examples/sentinel2_venus_corumba_odc.ipynb)
4. Using odc-stac to query and comparing the NDVI between Sentinel-2 and Mosaics during the year 2021 over Brazil [Compare Sentinel-2 and Mosaics NDVI](https://github.com/earthdaily/EDA-Documentation/blob/gh-pages/EDS%20Compatibility%20Examples/Sentinel2_Mosaics_Brazil_v2.ipynb)
